name: kerkoapp
description: A basic image for getting started with KerkoApp.
full_description:
[KerkoApp](https://github.com/whiskyechobravo/kerkoapp) is a web application that provides a faceted search interface for bibliographies managed with Zotero. 

[More details on using this image](https://github.com/whiskyechobravo/kerkoapp#running-from-docker).
